text.tspan: Global average long-term atmospheric concentration of carbon dioxide (CO₂), measured in parts per million (ppm).
Long-term trends in CO₂ concentrations can be measured at high-resolution using preserved air samples from ice
Source: EPICA Dome C CO₂ record (2015) & NOAA (2018)
